PrecisAmendments to the NATIONAL PARKS HIGHWAY TRAFFIC REGULATIONS which replace the per-vehicle permit fees with individual admission fees and make the fines for speeding match the ones prescribed by the province in which the offence occurs.

precis:
Amendments to the NATIONAL PARKS HIGHWAY TRAFFIC REGULATIONS which replace
the per-vehicle permit fees with individual admission fees and make the
fines for speeding match the ones prescribed by the province in which the
offence occurs.
